headline: Gen to Present at the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference
summary: Gen Digital Inc. (NASDAQ: GEN), a global leader dedicated to powering Digital Freedom, today announced that Vincent Pilette, Chief Executive Officer of Gen, and Natalie Derse, Chief Financial Officer of Gen, will participate in a fireside chat at the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference on Tuesday, March 3.
